{"lastModified":1776234188974,"uri":"c::8864389904::vessel::aa167700-5e23-11ef-88ef-99b0f5a4c0bf","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Base / Home Port: Sydney, Whitsundays, & Port Douglas\nOperating Area: Australia\n\nLUMIR is a 37.00m / 121ft Luxury Motor Superyacht built in 2005 by Heesen and later underwent a refit in 2013. Sleeping 10 guests in 4 cabins and with a crew of 6. Cruising at 13.50 kn/ph with a top speed of 31.00 kn/ph. The guest cabins comprise a master cabin, two VIP cabins and a twin bunk convertible.","blueprint":{"name":"LUMIR","images":["/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::aa167700-5e23-11ef-88ef-99b0f5a4c0bf::assets::14fdaec0-18f1-11f0-a25c-01c65298a657/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::aa167700-5e23-11ef-88ef-99b0f5a4c0bf::assets::39ce9430-18f1-11f0-a25c-01c65298a657/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::aa167700-5e23-11ef-88ef-99b0f5a4c0bf::assets::3cda2680-18f1-11f0-a25c-01c65298a657/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::aa167700-5e23-11ef-88ef-99b0f5a4c0bf::assets::1e9a9ec1-18f1-11f0-a25c-01c65298a657/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::aa167700-5e23-11ef-88ef-99b0f5a4c0bf::assets::1e9aece0-18f1-11f0-a25c-01c65298a657/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::aa167700-5e23-11ef-88ef-99b0f5a4c0bf::assets::44f6df20-18f1-11f0-a25c-01c65298a657/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::aa167700-5e23-11ef-88ef-99b0f5a4c0bf::assets::44f865c0-18f1-11f0-a25c-01c65298a657/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::aa167700-5e23-11ef-88ef-99b0f5a4c0bf::assets::8ec11991-18f1-11f0-a25d-01c65298a657/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::aa167700-5e23-11ef-88ef-99b0f5a4c0bf::assets::44f00150-18f1-11f0-a25c-01c65298a657/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::aa167700-5e23-11ef-88ef-99b0f5a4c0bf::assets::8ecba0e0-18f1-11f0-a816-7d2000757ead/{imageVaria